Special thanks to Rick Noack for the valuable insights, to ‪@valilevi for traveling to Afghanistan for us and the Afghan Crew and Secret Compass for their support (https://secretcompass.com/).

We travel to Afghanistan to investigate how a Taliban highway in the Wakhan Corridor could expand China's influence and change global trade.
